<p><b>How to add Plant 3D to AutoCAD?</b> Downloading and installing the corresponding Plant 3D Object Enabler from the Autodesk Account, will enable the proper display of Plant 3D related data within other AutoCAD products, including AutoCAD MEP. Simply open the DWG from Plant 3D in AutoCAD MEP after the Object Enabler has been installed.</p>
